verse = \lyricmode {
  Lord, what is man, mere man, that you should e -- ven
take note of him as you look down from heav -- en?
For he is but a breath, a puff of wind,
a fleet -- ing sha -- dow. Soon his days will end.
Lord, split the skies! Come down, make moun -- tains trem -- ble.
Come and so touch them that they smoke and rum -- ble.
Flash forth your lightning and fight my fight.
Shoot forth your ar -- rows. Put my foes to flight.
}
